get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/credit-limit-wallet/get-my-wallet
  body: none
  auth: inherit
}

docs {
  ### Get My Wallet
  Retrieves the credit limit wallet of the currently authenticated user.
  
  **Authentication:**
  - Requires a valid Bearer token.
  - The `id` in the token is used to find the corresponding wallet.
}
